\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the game's storyline, flying through imaginative worlds as Yuki, the Space Ranger. <br>Collect power-ups to strengthen your character, facing increasingly challenging levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Endless Mode</strong> <br>Battle relentless waves of enemies, scoring points for the Global Leaderboard. <br>A challenge for skilled players—do you have what it takes?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184500/extras/1b9eba2f984785b86ed1490f219db518.avif?t=1748449113\" width=600 height=82 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184500/extras/a46c23bc5944d8536579dbc388a99f7c.poster.avif?t=1748449113\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184500/extras/a46c23bc5944d8536579dbc388a99f7c.webm?t=1748449113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184500/extras/a46c23bc5944d8536579dbc388a99f7c.mp4?t=1748449113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184500/extras/95a9061ba39c2720c152b080734df479.avif?t=1748449113\" width=600 height=82 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184500/extras/a431868c84409dd33992c84b502f3981.poster.avif?t=1748449113\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184500/extras/a431868c84409dd33992c84b502f3981.webm?t=1748449113\" type=\"